<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title><%= school.name %> - SchoolHub</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/common.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/school.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <%- include("partials/header", { school: typeof school !== "undefined" ? school : null }) %>
  <main class="container">
    <a href="/" class="back-link">← 학교 선택으로 돌아가기</a>

    <header class="school-header">
      <h1><%= school.name %> 커뮤니티</h1>
      <p>이곳은 <%= school.name %> 학생들을 위한 커뮤니티입니다.</p>
    </header>

    <section class="school-dashboard">
      <div class="menu-grid two-cards">
        <a href="/schools/<%= school.slug %>/posts" class="menu-card board-card">
          <span class="card-badge">입장하기</span>
          <h2>게시판</h2>
          <p>학생들이 자유롭게 글을 작성하고 소통하는 공간</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/schools/<%= school.slug %>/lost-items" class="menu-card">
            <span class="card-badge">입장하기</span>
            <h2>분실물</h2>
            <p>분실물 등록 및 확인 기능</p>
        </a>
      </div>

      <aside class="notice-panel">
        <div class="notice-panel-header">
          <div>
            <span class="notice-label">NOTICE</span>
            <h2>공지사항</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="notice-list">
          <% if (notices.length === 0) { %>
            <div class="notice-empty">
              아직 등록된 공지사항이 없습니다.
            </div>
          <% } else { %>
            <% notices.forEach(notice => { %>
              <a
                href="/schools/<%= school.slug %>/notices/<%= notice.id %>"
                class="notice-title-link"
              >
                <%= notice.title %>
              </a>
            <% }) %>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </section>
  </main>
  <%- include("partials/footer") %>
</body>
</html>